predictions.article: Grain markets dip weighed by fallout from US tariff moves
predictions.prediction: The imposition of additional tariffs on imported chicken, wheat, corn, and cotton will lead to an increase in domestic prices for these commodities by at least 5% within the next month.
The projected trade deficit and new tariffs will result in a decrease in US agricultural export volumes by at least 10% by the end of the second quarter of 2025.
